DroidCam Privacy Policy and Terms of Use
This document governs your use of the software application "DroidCam/X (Classic)" [1, 2], "DroidCam Webcam & OBS Camera" [3, 4] for mobile devices,
corresponding companion software ("PC Clients"), other related components and written material
available on the Google Play Store, the Apple App Store, the dev47apps.com and droidcam.app websites (collectively "Application").
Privacy Policy
1. The Application does not collect any personal information.
2. The Application enables audio and video data to be streamed directly to connected client programs,
and you are fully responsible for all information contained within the audio and video streams.
In most cases, these audio and video streams are contained within your local network and not accessible externally.
Enabling external access requires manual steps and should be done at
users own risk
.
Opt Out:
You can erase data stored by the Application by uninstalling the Application. You may use the standard uninstall processes as may be available on your system.
Some data, such as configuration files or saved JPEG frames may get left behind due to inconsistencies with the uninstall processes.
Automatic Data Collection and Advertising:
The Application may incorporate third party analytics tools to help understand how the Application is being used, such as the frequency and duration of usage.
The Application may incorporate third party advertisers and third party advertising networks, who need to know how you interact with advertising provided in
the Application which helps keep the cost of the Application low. Advertisers and advertising networks may collect additional information within the Application context,
including, but not limited to, the unique identification ID of your mobile device, anonymous information about other applications you've downloaded to your mobile device,
your non-precise location information, and other non-precise information in order to help analyze and serve anonymous targeted advertising on the Application and elsewhere.
Changes and Consent:
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time for various reasons.
You are advised to consult this Privacy Policy regularly for any changes, as continued use is deemed approval of all changes.
If you have any questions regarding privacy while using the Application please e-mail privacy [at] dev47apps.com.
